To convert the [[sample rate]] of audio files in [[Digital Performer]] open the soundbites window, ('''Project/Soundbites''') then choose the audio files (soundbites) you want to convert. Then go to the soundbites window mini menu and choose '''Convert Sample Rate or Format'''

[[File:Digital Performer change sample rate of soundbite.png]]



Set the settings you want then click '''OK'''.


